creator: 3B Products
descriptionHtml:
3B MaskFitter is a revolutionary new way to conveniently help choose PAP mask selections for the device user’s lifestyle. Based on decades of patient data and built to platform biometric facial recognition software, 3B MaskFitter scans facial geometry to determine appropriate cushion size and narrow down mask type.

3B MaskFitter is available for customers and patients of the 3B2GO program and for any customer of 3B Medical, Inc. This easy to use app was designed to augment professional medical sizing for PAP masks and is not meant as a substitute for that purpose.

3B Medical’s masks are designed to be lightweight and comfortable, easing the transition into sleep breathing therapy.

3B MaskFitter currently supports the following mask selection:

· Rio II Nasal Pillow Mask
· Viva Nasal Mask
· Siesta Nasal Mask
· Siesta FullFace Mask
· Numa FullFace Mask
descriptionShort: 3B Mask Fitter is the remote tool to help patients with mask choice and sizing.
